{
  "texts": [
    "For instance, training a model using 4,000 samples incurred a data collection cost of $32 and a training cost of $0.35, resulting in a total cost of $32.35.",
    "The model achieves an average agreement of around 70%.",
    "It costs $0.005 to identify an effectively malicious query.",
    "Assuming we need to identify 10,000 effectively malicious queries, the total cost would be $82. 35.",
    "However, training the model with 2,000 samples and 6,000 samples would incur costs of $91 and $92.8, respectively."
  ]
}